<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/55227.Failed_States"><img alt="Failed States: The Abuse of Power and the Assault on Democracy" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1405971629l/55227._SX98_.jpg" />
